The Saudi Arabia’s Ambassador to Nigeria, Mr Adnan Bostaji, is dead. Bostaji was said to have died in his sleep at the early hours of Tuesday. A statement from the Royal Embassy of Saudi Arabia in Abuja said: “With the deepest sense of sadness and complete submission to the will of Allah, Royal Embassy announces the passing away of His Excellency, the Ambassador of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia to Nigeria, Mr. Adnan Mahmoud Bostaji. May his blessed soul rest in peace.”